<snippet>
	<content><![CDATA[const initializeArrayWithValues = (n, val = 0) => Array(n).fill(val);]]></content>
	<description>Initializes and fills an array with the specified values.  Use `Array(n)` to create an array of the desired length, `fill(v)` to fill it with the desired values. You can omit `val` to use a default value of `0`.</description>
